\## 📓 Notebooks



| Notebook | Description | Key Output |

|----------|-------------|------------|

| `01\_EDA\_BigQuery.ipynb` | SQL EDA on 3M+ rows, 12 queries, 7 visualizations | Business insights, feature hypotheses |

| `02\_Feature\_Engineering.ipynb` | PySpark feature pipeline, 60+ features, leakage prevention | train\_features.parquet, test\_features.parquet |

| `03\_Model\_Training.ipynb` | 5 model comparison, evaluation, business impact calculation | best\_model\_lgbm.pkl, results |



